Definition: someone who claims to speak the truth
Example: a bold asserter; a declarer of his intentions; affirmers of traditional doctrine; an asseverator of strong convictions; an avower of his own great intelligence
Synonyms: verb, communication, assert, declarer, declare, affirmer, affirm, asseverator, asseverate, avower, avow, communicator, someone, who, claims, to, speak, the, truth, a, bold, of, his, intentions, affirmers, traditional, doctrine, an, strong, convictions, own, great, intelligence
Category: noun.person
